<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, orange, rgb(113, 113, 228));
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            
        }
        .container {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            max-width: 1000px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .item {
            background-color: #e7e7e7;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            flex: 1 1 300px; /* Flex-grow, flex-shrink, flex-basis */
            max-width: 300px;
        }
        .item h1 {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .item p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
        }
        .diagonalimg{
            width: 100%;
            height: 100vh;
            background-image: linear-gradient(to top left, rgb(6,6,64) 50%, white 50%);
            padding-left: 500px;
            padding-top: 300px;
            
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <form method="post" action="/features">
        
    <div class="container">
        <div class="item">
            <h1>Games</h1>
            <p>The admin can create games, and the games are available for players to play.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <h1>Create Sessions</h1>
            <p>Anyone who wants to create a session can create it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <h1>Join Sessions</h1>
            <p>The admin has the right to create and delete sessions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <h1>Change Of Password</h1>
            <p>Users can change their password if they want.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <h1>User Integrity</h1>
            <p>We save user details and passwords in an encrypted way.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <h1>Match Schedules</h1>
            <p>Never miss a game with our comprehensive schedules.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</form>
</body>
</html>
